// WORKING NAME: "Empowered Reach" (placeholder — needs naming pass)
// Ability: blood_boil
// Rarity: Rare
// Uniqueness: Exclusive
//
// Effect: Behavior hook "blood_boil_dnd_range".
//
// Hook behavior (registered in AbilityPlugin):
//   Reads PlayerZonePresence (zone/components.rs).
//   If presence.is_inside("death_and_decay"):
//     Doubles the "range" param before the blood_boil behavior executes (Pre hook).
//   Otherwise: no effect.
//
// This demonstrates the zone-presence pattern without modifying D&D or the base
// blood_boil ability definition. The zone interaction is encoded entirely in this hook.
//
// Listed in blood_boil.ron under hooks: [(Pre, "blood_boil_dnd_range")].
(
    id: "blood_boil_dnd_range_rare",
    display_name: "Empowered Reach",
    ability_scope: Some("blood_boil"),
    rarity: Rare,
    uniqueness: Exclusive,
    effect: Behavior("blood_boil_dnd_range"),
)
